io.github.bigbio.pgatk.io.common

Interface MzIterableReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterator<Spectrum>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IClusterSourceReader
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AplIndexedReader, ClusteringFileReader, MgfIndexedReader, MgfIterableReader, MspIterableReader, MzMlIndexedReader, MzXMLIterableReader, PrideJsonIterableReader

    public interface MzIterableReader
extends Serializable, Iterator<Spectrum>
    The MzIterableReader is an interface that only provides methods to read one Spectrum after another This interface and the classes behind allow to read an entire file without needs to index the entire file. For indexed and random access to peak list files please use the JmzReader interface.
    Author:
    yperez
